Current Team &quot;Thirsty Chimpmunks&quot; (we&#039;r only bronze 5) ; a fun casual team consisting of bronze to plat players. Its a fun team but we play kinda serious in rank games . Just looking for more to join the team; any role. This is not a serious team; it can act as a training for other rank team/solo ranking. We use skype, and decide to change the match up as 4 of our 9 members have taken a break from League.

If keen; write a small discription of yourself, we also play normals for fun. No rages and kids (sorry, but have had bad experience with them in game). Let me know IGN, age, pref roles and something interesting about yourselves. Or add Frostwolf77; but its better if I read it here so I can ask my friends to also make a decision. We&#039;r all withing age 19 to 24.

